B.atR=new A.cw("How do I export my sessions?","Go to the Sessions tab and tap the Import/Export button in the top-right. Choose Export, select CSV or Excel format, and the file will be generated and ready to save or share. CSV works with any spreadsheet app; Excel exports a formatted .xlsx file.")
B.au3=new A.cw("How do I import sessions from a spreadsheet?","Tap Import on the Import/Export screen and pick a CSV or Excel file from your device. TableLab will show a column mapping UI \u2014 drag or assign your spreadsheet's columns to the correct session fields. Confirm the mapping and the sessions will be imported.")
